@-moz-document url-prefix("http://www.tumblr.com/"), url-prefix("https://www.tumblr.com/") {
/* ----------------------------------------------------------

	BLUE HYDRANGEAS IN THE GARBAGE PILE OF TUMBLR

	Dashboard Theme for Tumblr

		by Rachael [@rhaegara]

	VERSION 2.1.5 // last updated May 13th, 2016

 -------------------------------------------------------------

	Remember to leave a positive review if you like this
	style. Thank you!!

 -------------------------------------------------------------

	IMPORTANT: This style does not work with the following
	XKit extensions:

		- Themes / Themes+ / Theme Editor

		- Unreverse (post buttons)

		- Tweaks
			- Add a separator line for Tag section on editor
			- Use a real red on notifications and post like
			  buttons
			- Show Chat posts in classic interface
			- Slim sidebar buttons

		- XInbox
			- Slim Incoming Fan Mail

	Please disable these extension settings while using.

 -------------------------------------------------------------
 
	NEW UPDATES WITH VERSION 2.1.5
    
    	- Bug fix to remove background color of recommended posts
 
	NEW UPDATES WITH VERSION 2.1.4
    
    	- Bug fixes after Tumblr changed their icons

	NEW UPDATES WITH VERSION 2.1.3
    
    	- NEW! Option to use your own custom colors
    	- Bug fixes for the newest Tumblr updates
    	- Made a few alterations to the Message function

	NEW UPDATES WITH VERSION 2.1.2
    
    	- Bug fixes for the newest Tumblr updates
        - Search bar has been fixed up a bit

	NEW UPDATES WITH VERSION 2.1.1

		- Bug fixes for the newest Tumblr updates
		- Slimmer style for the Link posts
		- Font fixes (for the Custom Font options)

	NEW UPDATES WITH VERSION 2.1.0

		- NEW! More fonts choices are available
          
	NEW UPDATES WITH VERSION 2.0.1

		- Bug fixes to combat Tumblr's minor tweaks
		- Some improvements to the Explore page to make it
          less terrible (it's still kinda bad though)

	NEW UPDATES WITH VERSION 2.0.0

		- Code has been re-organized so it's easier to read
		- Now works with the April 9th, 2015 Tumblr update
		- Now works with XKit extension: Post Archiver

 ---------------------------------------------------------- */
}

@-moz-document url-prefix("http://www.tumblr.com/"), url-prefix("https://www.tumblr.com/") {
/* ------------------------------------------

 THIS SECTION CHANGES NOTHING BUT THE COLORS

------------------------------------------ */

